lead_paragraph: AUSTIN--Joyce Phillips, passed from cardiac failure, September 10, 1923 - March 21, 2016. Former Executive Vice President of the Federation of Protestant Welfare Agencies, NYC, served the Diocese of New York and Episcopal Church and was longtime vestryman of Trinity Church. Survived by her sister, Dr. Mildred Phillips and her niece, Ms. Tippi Brooke Phillips. Services at Trinity Church, Broadway and Wall Streets, Tuesday, March 29 at 10:00am. 1/3
